NAME
       man - display a manual page

SYNOPSIS
       man PAGE

DESCRIPTION
       Display the manual page for a command (e.g. 'man ls') or
       for 'theleberton'.

       Manual pages are stored as plain files under mans/, one
       per page.

SEE ALSO
       help(1), ls(1)

